   "body" : "Every thread, being counted in `CCheckQueue::nIdle`, is counted in `CCheckQueue::nTotal` as well. That makes possible the [sum](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/65de8eeeca29e71378aa34602b287ab921b040e4/src/checkqueue.h#L113) `(nTotal + nIdle + 1)` exceeds the number of all threads available for a `CCheckQueue` instance, which is unreasonable.",
